legacy.full_text: On September 4, 2023, Ambassador Zhao Weiping, accompanied by Counselor Wei Jinming, paid an official visit to Zambezi Region. During the visit, Ambassador Zhao met with Hon. Colonel (Rtd) Lawrence Alufea Sampofu, Governor of Zambezi Region ...

legacy.full_text: On August 17, President Xi Jinping, presided over the meeting of the Standing Committee of the Political Bureau of the Communist Party of China (CPC) Central Committee and delivered an speech on flood prevention and relief as well as post-disaster restoration and reconstruction.

legacy.description: Embassy of the People's Republic of China in the Republic of Namibia
legacy.name: Chinese Embassy in Namibia

legacy.full_text: On August 18, Ambassador Zhao Weiping attended and addressed the opening ceremony of 2023 Huawei Seeds for the Future ICT Student Training Program which was held at the Namibia University of Science and Technology.

legacy.description: Embassy of the People's Republic of China in the Republic of Namibia
legacy.name: Chinese Embassy in Namibia

legacy.full_text: The Hon. Dr. Peya Mushelenga, Minister of Information & Communication Technologies, Dr. Erold Naomab, Vice Chancellor of NUST, Mr. Michael Zhang, Huawei Namibia Managing Director attended the ceremony, and 25 Namibian university students participated in this training.

legacy.description: Embassy of the People's Republic of China in the Republic of Namibia
legacy.name: Chinese Embassy in Namibia

legacy.full_text: In his remarks, Ambassador Zhao Weiping expressed support for Huawei Seeds for the Future program and encouraged the Chinese companies in Namibia to contribute more to Namibia’s social and economic development. https://t.co/SjQX3s7WpG

legacy.full_text: On August 7, 2023, Ambassador Zhao Weiping paid a courtesy call on Hon. Anna Nghipondoka, Minister of Education, Arts and Culture of the Republic of Namibia. Amb. Zhao briefed Hon. Nghipondoka on his recent visits to some primary and middle schools in Namibia ...

legacy.description: Embassy of the People's Republic of China in the Republic of Namibia
legacy.name: Chinese Embassy in Namibia

legacy.full_text: ... and expressed the Embassy’s willingness to join the Ministry of Education in promoting relevant cooperative programs and provide assistance for the development of Namibia’s education wherever it can.

legacy.description: Embassy of the People's Republic of China in the Republic of Namibia
legacy.name: Chinese Embassy in Namibia

legacy.full_text: Hon. Nghipondoka said, China and Namibia are good friends. China has over the years provided active support for Namibia’s education infrastructure building, having demonstrated its friendship to the Namibian people, of which she is appreciative. https://t.co/xbBWJfJqwQ
